#Welcome to Chess Online
this Chess-Game was developed by students as part of the Web-Technologies Lecture at [HTWG Konstanz](http://www.htwg-konstanz.de).

Just click on *New Game* to start playing and share the URL to play against others. You can also create an account, or login with your Google Account, by clicking on *Login/Register*. This gives you the advantage to get a list of all your games.



Chess-Online
============

WebTec project for AIN.

In order to run the project you need a MongoDB running on the same server as the play project. Each game instance gets a uuid assigned and is stored in the MongoDB.